input.product_name: Buffalo Blizzard Bottom Drain Kit for Above-ground Swimming Pools Up To 30 Round
input.description: The Buffalo Blizzard Bottom Drain Kit is an all-you-need solution to replacing the bottom drain of your above-ground swimming pool. The 4-way valve gives you the control and ease of directing your water. This kit includes 2 bottom drains with a safe anti-vortex cover, a 4-way ball valve, 25 of 1½" flexible PVC hose, quick disconnect fittings for easy winterizing, instructions and all necessary clamps and fittings. The Buffalo Blizzard Bottom Drain Kit will fit above-ground pools up to 30 round. Instructions: Locate the center of the pool and install center drains at least 3 apart from one another. Dig a trench 4" to 6" deep. The trench should lead out and under the bottom channel of the pool to the area where the filter will be set. Connect the hose to the fittings and bottom main drains, using teflon tape on all threads. Clamps should grip on the ridged portion of fittings. Before packing the trench with dirt, tape over the main drain openings and screw holes so as not to get dirt into screw holes. Do not pack the trench with sand. Leave hose at least 6" long on the outside pool wall for hooking up to the filter. Check with local codes to see if this hose length needs to be longer. Features: 2 bottom drains with a safe anti-vortex cover, 25 of 1½" flexible PVC hose, quick disconnect fittings for easy winterizing, instructions and all necessary clamps and fittings The 4-way valve gives you the control and ease of directing your water Designed to fit above-ground pools up to 30 round 2 bottom drains with a safe anti-vortex cover, 25 of 1½" flexible PVC hose, quick disconnect fittings for easy winterizing, instructions and all necessary clamps and fittingsThe 4-way valve gives you the control and ease of directing your waterDesigned to fit above-ground pools up to 30 round

input.description: The Mega Tropical Purple Marble Inflatable Water Slide Bounce House Combo is the perfect addition to any backyard celebration or outdoor event. With gender-neutral colors that are bright and attractive, this inflatable jumper can be used for both boys or girls events. These special inflatable water slide bounce house combos have it all, featuring a spacious bouncing area where kids can run, jump and play to their hearts delight before heading down the connected water slide and finishing in the splash pool at the base. The slides built-in misting system connects easily to any standard garden hose and ensures that the slide stays wet for some cool fun on a hot day. You can even use the slide without water on a cooler day and its just as much fun! Pogo Inflatables are designed with the highest safety measures and ultimate durability in mind. This commercial grade inflatable is constructed with 15oz PVC vinyl with additional vinyl patches sewn in at all stress points to allow for maximum strength, durability and most importantly, safety. All seams have been triple-threaded and heat-welded for superior durability and these measures also prevent water from entering the unit, as well as from dirt and sand causing damage to the seams, thus prolonging the life of your inflatable and minimizing repairs. This unit features a "Gator Mouth" system that alleviates pressure at 90-degree stress points, adding just another layer of durability to your unit and extending its longevity through the wear and tear of a busy rental season. The landing area at the base of the water slide features a built-in drain that will help keep water levels appropriate for children of all ages. The enclosed roof offers some UV protection for kids while being out in the sun and also has a marked escape hatch for emergencies. The slide features our "No Jump Top" design with finger-safe netting that ensures children slide safely and correctly every time. The walls of the bounce house also feature this same finger-safe netting that allows a window inside the unit for proper supervision of children at play. The unit has commercial-grade webbing and velcro throughout and zippers for easy deflation when its time to pack up at the end of the day. This Inflatable Bounce House has a maximum weight limit of 1000 lbs, so it is recommended that only 6 participants are active on the unit at any given time. These inflatables are easy to set up and offer a 1-year limited manufacturers warranty. These are not the types of units that you are going to be dragging to the curb after one season. The commercial-grade quality of this inflatable will give you the peace of mind of having a sound and safe structure that gives children that one-of-a-kind lift that they get from jumping around and playing together. THE POGO PROMISE: You can have ultimate trust that our inflatables adopt the absolute highest level safety possible, complying with ASTM and CPSC guidelines for residential or commercial use. Our commercial inflatables are constructed from high-quality, heavy-duty 15oz Vinyl that is quadruple reinforced and has an extra layer of vinyl sewn in at stress points for longer usable life and for added safety. That very same vinyl construction is contaminant-free (Lead/Phthalates, Etc) and compiles with the Lead-Free Toys Act. Our Inflatables only utilize heavy-duty, commercial-grade webbing and velcro. Our inflatables also have a zipper for easy deflation, as well as granting easy access to the inside of the unit. input.product_name: Heavy-Duty 4 x 8 Winterizing Air Pillow for Above-Ground Swimming Pools
input.description: The Pool Mate Deluxe Winterizing Air Pillow absorbs stress created by ice building up in your pool. As ice expands in your pool the pressure created is exerted onto the pillow instead of the walls of your pool. Ice equalizer pillows are an essential way to protect your pool during the winter. The pillow will pop before the ice damages your pool. Ice Equalizer pillows also reduce the build-up of rain water, leaves and snow on your winter cover. All you have to do is inflate the pillow and place it under your cover during the winter months. Do not overfill the pillow with air, as this can cause the valve to pop out during the winter months. Smaller equalizer pillows are recommended for round pools and larger equalizer pillows are recommended for oval pools. Using additional pillows will protect your pool if one fails. Using additional pillows may require a larger than expected pool cover size. input.product_name: Robelle 1 Gallon Algaecide for Swimming Pools
input.description: Robelle Algaecide is an efficient and economical way to improve the appearance and cleanliness of your pool. It can be added directly to the pool or to the water circulating equipment. Economically priced, Robelle Algaecide can be stored for prolonged periods of time without losing its efficacy. Initial dosage: add one gallon of this product per 25,000 gallons of pool water. Routine dosage: add one quart of this product per 25,000 gallons every three to five days. Available for sale in either 1 quart containers or 1 gallon containers. Purchase gallon container as 1 or 4 packs or quarts as 1, 2 or 4 packs to save you even more money. input.product_name: Kids Beach Sand Toys Set for Gift with Sand Molds,Mesh Bag, Sand Wheel,Tool Play Set, Watering Can, Shovels, Rakes, Bucket ,Sea Creatures, Castle Molds 18 PCs F-129
input.description: Educational: Because sand is an excellent tool for enhancing kids sensory experiences, adding this beach sand toy set will augment the fun and the learning experience. The opportunity to create and build with all the molds and tools is what gets the imagination moving. Kids are given the freedom to create and foster knowledge through reflection because they will be thinking about structure, size and aesthetics without realizing. For young children, playing with this beach sand toy set can help exercise their hands-on capacity. Since the pieces are easily identifiable and of corresponding color to their prototype, children can also learn the names and qualities of sea creatures, for instance. Socialization/Collaboration: When kids are creating be it castles, sea horses, etc. they are willing and even eager to discuss their creations. Indeed, sand and this beach set is a great place for socialization, for kids will be learning to share, communicate, and be exposed to someone elses version of creativity. Moreover, parents and guardians are welcome to join in the fun; they can come up with different activities or join their little architects. Perfect Gift: Be it a sunny day at the beach, a sandbox at the park or a sandbox in your backyard, this beach set is ideal for any of these occasions. For this reason, this gift is not limited to any occasion, holiday or birthday present! It will particularly thrill kids who love the ocean, the castles and sea animals. However, it could be that your kid has yet to discover that love for the sand until the opportunity is given. Includes: a bucket, water wheel, water can, 2 rakes (1 big and 1 small), 3 shovels (2 small and 1 big), drain shovel, and 9 molds (seahorse, starfish, fish, duck, turtle, whale, shell, crab, castle). Perfect Gift: If your kids love the beach and the sand, then this beach set is the perfect gift! You can, of course, dig, shape, smooth and even carry water with nothing but your own two hands. But having the right equipment this beach set will make your sand-castling experience infinitely more pleasurable. Packaging: The beach set comes in a blue drawstring bag to conveniently store all the pieces and carry it as a backpack anywhere you go. Also, the water wheel can be easily attached and detached from the bucket, making it more convenient for storage and castle-making. Durable: The pieces of this beach set are made of high quality and environmental friendly material, which makes them sturdy, durable and thus safer not only for your kids, but for the environment as well. Meaning, the pieces of this set will not easily brake and they will retain their color even after hours of sun exposure. Precautions: Because the beach sand toy set does not include small pieces, there is no choking hazard, so anyone can join in the fun. There are also no sharp edges or parts in any of the pieces. input.product_name: Sodium Thiosulfate Pentahydrate Na2O3S2 – Dechlorinator for Pool, Pond - 5 Lbs
input.description: Sodium Thiosulfate Pentahydrate - Na2O3S2 – 5 Pounds: Sodium thiosulfate has numerous uses in a wide variety of areas: as a dechlorinator of pools, hot tubs, ponds and aquariums, for agriculture and aquaculture, as a photographic fixer, in the medical world, and on a large scale in certain industries such as paper production and gold-mining. input.product_name: In The Swim Pool Chlorine Stabilizer and Conditioner - 25 Pound Bucket
input.description: Chlorine stabilizer reduces chlorine loss caused by the suns ultraviolet rays. Adding stabilizer greatly increases chlorine effectiveness and can actually cut chlorine consumption by up to 25% a year. 100% Cyanuric Acid. Dosage: Use 1 pound per 3,000 gallons for 40ppm stabilizer, 1 pound per 4000 gallons for 30 ppm stabilizer. Do not over-dose, it is important to gradually increase the stabilizer level as it is very difficult to reduce once it has gotten too high. Stabilizer levels should be maintained at 30-50ppm. In The Swim Pool Chlorine Stabilizer and Conditioner - 25 lb. Pail

input.description: The Pool Blaster Battery-Powered Water Tech Pool Vacuum LVAC100 is completely self-contained and does not require the use of a garden hose. input.product_name: HTH Algae Guard 30 Algaecide for Swimming Pools, 38-Ounces
input.description: This is a concentrated, non-foaming algaecide product that, when used regularly, will prevent and kill the growth of green, black and yellow algae. At the beginning of the season when opening your pool add 8oz of product for each 10,000 gallons of water in your pool for an Initial Dose. For a maintenance dose, add 2oz every 5 days for the same 10,000 gallon pool size. If the pool has slight visible algae growth, treat with the "Initial Dose." Vacuum pool after 24 hours to remove algae debris. If visible algae are still present or re-appear, repeat this treatment as necessary. When pool is free of visible algae, use the "Maintenance Dose." This is a concentrated, non-foaming algaecide product that, when used regularly, will prevent and kill the growth of green, black and yellow algae

input.product_name: HTH Blue Sparkle Skimmer Tabs unstabilized sanitizer for Swimming Pools, 5.5 lbs
input.description: Keep your indoor or outdoor pool clean and clear with HTH Blue Sparkle Skimmer Tabs. Just use in your pool skimmer to destroy bacteria and organic contaminants without adding additional cyanuric acid (CYA) to the water that can lead to overstabilizing your pool. HTH Blue Sparkle Skimmer Tabs feature an innovated patented technology that provides long-lasting, slow-dissolving chlorination without adding extra cyanuric acid (CYA).   DIRECTIONS Use only in skimmer and skimmer basket. Skimmer basket should be free of all other water treatment products before adding the recommended number of Blue Sparkle Skimmer Tabs. Place skimmer tab in the empty skimmer basket. Use one tab of the product per 10,000 gallons of pool water. After one day of use, test free available chlorine (FAC) residual with HTH Multi-purpose 6-Way Test Strips, sold separately. Do not enter pool until the free available chlorine residual is 1 to 4 ppm (parts per million). Contains one 5.5-pound pail of Blue Sparkle Skimmer Tabs for swimming pools Long-lasting sanitization against bacteria, algae and other organisms Does not contain cyanuric acid (CYA) or contribute to the buildup of stabilizer that makes chlorine less effective Slow-dissolving yet fast-acting chlorination Compatible with chlorine and salt water pools Contains one 5.5-pound pail of Blue Sparkle Skimmer Tabs for swimming poolsLong-lasting sanitization against bacteria, algae and other organismsDoes not contain cyanuric acid (CYA) or contribute to the buildup of stabilizer that makes chlorine less effectiveSlow-dissolving yet fast-acting chlorinationCompatible with chlorine and salt water pools

input.product_name: No Mor Muriatic Acid Swimming Pool pH Reducer - 2.5 Pounds
input.description: No Mor Muriatic Acid Swimming Pool pH Reducer - 2.5 Pounds. No Mor Muriatic Acid is a granular chemical designed to slowly lower the pH and alkalinity of swimming pool water so you never have to use muriatic acid again. It is safer to handle and use than liquid acids and more efficient. One 2.5 pound granular bottle is equivalent to 1 gallon of muriatic acid. No Mor Muriatic Acid is fast dissolving and especially great for pools with chlorine generators. Directions for use: Always adjust total alkalinity first because high total alkalinity will create an almost constant acid demand. Dissolve or pre-dilute No Mor Muriatic Acid in a bucket of water first, then broadcast into the deep end of the pool when not in use with pump and filter running. Never add more than 1.5 pounds of this product per 10,000 gallons at any one time. Allow pool water to recirculate 2 hours and retest pH and repeat treatment as necessary. Wait one hour before swimming after treatment. If you routinely add 16 ounces of muriatic acid to lower the pH, you use 10 ounces of No Mor Muriatic Acid to gain the same results. If you add 1 quart then use 20 ounces of No Mor Muriatic Acid. CAUTION: Do not mix this product directly with any chlorinated chemical product or any oxidizer. Note: Product is a wet mix that may compact during shipping. Tap the container on a firm surface and shake to loosen before use. United Chemical No Mor Muriatic Acid - 2.5lbs. MURA-C12 No Mor Muriatic AcidÂ is the only alternative to liquid pool acid.No Mor Muriatic AcidÂ is a revolutionary new water balancer that offers all the benefits of liquid acid but none of the draw backs. input.product_name: Plastic Horseshoe and Ring Toss Game Set (2 in 1)
input.description: Plastic Horseshoe and Ring Toss Game Set (2 in 1) If you are looking for fun group games to play at a barbeque, picnic or other gathering, this Plastic Horseshoe and Ring Toss combo set is the perfect solution. Unlike other plastic horseshoe games, this set also comes with four ring toss rings so you can easily transition from one game to the other without removing any stakes or spending additional time setting up a playing field. Horseshoes and ring toss are easy games to play for adults and kids alike. They are a great activity for a carnival, or in a physical education class. The horseshoe components of this set include two green plastic stakes that measure 13.75 inches long, and four horseshoes that measure 6.5 inches tall and 5.125 inches wide. The horseshoes include one of each green, red, orange and blue. The four red ring toss rings have a 5 inch diameter. Both games within this set are recommended for ages 3 and up. To set up a horseshoe game outside, stakes should be driven into the ground about 40 feet apart and angled slightly towards each other. The stakes should stick out of the ground about 12 inches. When tossing horseshoes, the National Horseshoe Pitchers Association states that the foul line should be 27-37 feet away from the stake. If you want to make a more permanent backyard field by digging a 4-inch deep rectangular pit around each stake, measuring 31 inches wide and 43 inches long. Fill each pit with sand, sawdust or a fine filler substance. To play, flip a coin. The winner goes first. Each person tosses two horseshoes per inning, followed by his opponent. Once both players have tossed their shoes, scoring begins. Any shoe within 6 inches of the peg/stake gets one point. If one player has both shoes closer to the stake/peg than his opponent, that player is awarded two points. If a player gets a "leaner," or a shoe that falls upright against the stake/peg, that person is awarded one point. If a player gets a "ringer," or a shoe that completely circles the stake/peg, that player gets three points. If one player gets a ringer and has his other shoe closer to the peg/stake than his opponent, that player would be awarded a total of four points. If both players get ringers, the player with the shoe closest to the stake/peg gets one point, and the ringers cancel each other out. If there is a tie at the end of the game, an extra two innings are played to determine a winner. During game play, a tournament consists of 50 points, while a regular game contains 21 points.

input.product_name: Pogo Mega Inflatable Water Slide Bounce House Combo with Blower, Tropical
input.description: The Mega Tropical Inflatable Water Slide Bounce House Combo is the perfect addition to any backyard celebration or outdoor event. With gender-neutral colors that are bright and attractive, this inflatable jumper can be used for both boys or girls events. These special inflatable water slide bounce house combos have it all, featuring a spacious bouncing area where kids can run, jump and play to their hearts delight before heading down the connected water slide and finishing in the splash pool at the base. The slides built-in misting system connects easily to any standard garden hose and ensures that the slide stays wet for some cool fun on a hot day. You can even use the slide without water on a cooler day and its just as much fun! Pogo Inflatables are designed with the highest safety measures and ultimate durability in mind. This commercial grade inflatable is constructed with 15oz PVC vinyl with additional vinyl patches sewn in at all stress points to allow for maximum strength, durability and most importantly, safety. All seams have been triple-threaded and heat-welded for superior durability and these measures also prevent water from entering the unit, as well as from dirt and sand causing damage to the seams, thus prolonging the life of your inflatable and minimizing repairs. This unit features a "Gator Mouth" system that alleviates pressure at 90-degree stress points, adding just another layer of durability to your unit and extending its longevity through the wear and tear of a busy rental season. The landing area at the base of the water slide features a built-in drain that will help keep water levels appropriate for children of all ages. The enclosed roof offers some UV protection for kids while being out in the sun and also has a marked escape hatch for emergencies. The slide features our "No Jump Top" design with finger-safe netting that ensures children slide safely and correctly every time. The walls of the bounce house also feature this same finger-safe netting that allows a window inside the unit for proper supervision of children at play. The unit has commercial-grade webbing and velcro throughout and zippers for easy deflation when its time to pack up at the end of the day. This Inflatable Bounce House has a maximum weight limit of 1000 lbs, so it is recommended that only 6 participants are active on the unit at any given time. These inflatables are easy to set up and offer a 1-year limited manufacturers warranty. These are not the types of units that you are going to be dragging to the curb after one season. The commercial-grade quality of this inflatable will give you the peace of mind of having a sound and safe structure that gives children that one-of-a-kind lift that they get from jumping around and playing together. THE POGO PROMISE: You can have ultimate trust that our inflatables adopt the absolute highest level safety possible, complying with ASTM and CPSC guidelines for residential or commercial use. Our commercial inflatables are constructed from high-quality, heavy-duty 15oz Vinyl that is quadruple reinforced and has an extra layer of vinyl sewn in at stress points for longer usable life and for added safety. That very same vinyl construction is contaminant-free (Lead/Phthalates, Etc) and compiles with the Lead-Free Toys Act. Our Inflatables only utilize heavy-duty, commercial-grade webbing and velcro. Our inflatables also have a zipper for easy deflation, as well as granting easy access to the inside of the unit. Inflatable Water Slide Bounce House with Blower Includes bounce house blower, stakes, storage bag, vinyl patch repair kit Commercial grade PVC vinyl, ideal for bounce house rentals  Inflatable Water Slide Bounce House with BlowerIncludes bounce house blower, stakes, storage bag, vinyl patch repair kitCommercial grade PVC vinyl, ideal for bounce house rentals

input.product_name: HAYWARD VL40T32 VL Above Ground Swimming Pool Sand Filter w/ Pump System
input.description: The Hayward VL40T32S Pro Series sand system is designed and equipped to offer the ideal combination of energy efficiency and outstanding water clarity. A broad selection of filter sizes, pumps, and accessories allows you to choose and merchandise the system(s) that best suit your above-ground pool program. Sand filters are one of the most popular and cheap way to filter water. For good reason. They are simple, effective, and require very little attention. Pool water is routed through a sand-filled pressure vessel. In this method, impurities are extracted from the water using sand to collect and attract the debris as small as 20 to 40 microns. Over time, dirt accumulates in the spaces between the sand particles causing the pressure in the vessel to rise as water finds it harder to pass through. This signals you to "backwash" the filter. Simply reverse the water flow and "knock out" the dirt. - Hayward VL40T32S VL Series Above Ground Swimming Pool Sand Filter with Pump System. Determining Fence Size The amount of fencing each pool needs is determined by "fence sections" - the number of sections of your pool between uprights. One space between two uprights equals one fence section. All pool fences will require Base Kit A. Larger fences use Kits B and C to add on from there. input.product_name: Clean Sweep Muck & Debris Pond and Pool Vacuum
input.description: The Clean Sweep Muck & Debris Pond and Pool Vacuum is the fast, effective and convenient way to remove muck, debris and decaying organic matter from water gardens, fish ponds and swimming pools. The powerful 1400 watt motor produces a powerful vacuum, with its 6 foot maximum suction depth, that can dislodge and extract the toughest layers of settled sludge or decaying organic matter on the pond bottom. This unit operates on a continuous intermittent cycle. Heres what that means - once the vacuum fills the holding chamber the motor shuts off, the chamber drains, and the vacuum motor restarts. The unit cycles like this, continuously, until the job is done. The Clean Sweep Muck & Debris Pond and Pool Vacuum comes with a 13 foot intake suction hose, 4 extension tubes, 3 vacuum nozzles, a 6.5 foot outfeed hose and a debris collection bag. The debris collection bag attaches to the discharge end of the outfeed hose. Pond water, laden with decaying organic matter, makes excellent organic fertilizer for plants and shrubs. Simply attach the debris collection bag to the outfeed hose to capture the solids and allow nutrient rich pond water to flow into plantings. The compact design of the unit, with easy grip handle, is easy to lift and maneuver. 2 foot grounded power cord, 2-year manufacturers warranty Fast, effective and convenient way to remove muck, debris and decaying organic matter from water gardens, fish ponds and swimming pools Powerful 1400 watt motor, with its 6 foot maximum suction depth, can dislodge and extract the toughest layers of settled sludge or decaying organic matter on the pond bottom This unit operates on a continuous intermittent cycle. input.product_name: Rx Clear No Grab Tab 3" Chlorine Tabs with Water Soluble Wrapper - 22 lbs
input.description: Get prescription strength clarity with the Rx Clear No Grab Tab 3" chlorine tablets. Simply remove the tab from the bucket (leave it in the wrapper), place in your pool, and youre all set. Slow-dissolving, with a balance of 90% available chlorine and 99% Trichlor to stop algae and bacteria growth. Our tablets are stabilized with cyanuric acid, forming an iso-cyanurite. this gives them a longer shelf-life and less of an odor than other types of chlorine that utilize calcium hypochlorite. Additionally, the Rx Clear 3"" Stabilized Chlorine Tabs are UV protected against the harmful sun rays, which prevents chlorine burn-off in your swimming pool and reduces the number of pool chemicals you need to add, saving you money. Use 1 tablet per 5,000 gallons of water per week by adding the pool chlorine tablets to your pools skimmer and using the flow of your pump to dissolve and distribute the pool chemicals. Each chlorinating tablet is pH 2.7, weighs 7 oz. and is individually packaged to take the guessing out of how much chlorine to use in your pool and reduce the chemical mess. The Rx Clear 3" tablets require a dosage of only 1 tablet per 5,000 gallons of pool water. Each dosage lasts up to one week. Use the following formulas below to find out the number of gallons in your pool: Rectangular = Length x Width x Height x 7.5 Round = Diameter x Diameter x Height x 5.9 Oval = Length x Width x Height x 5.9 NOTE: Some of the tabs may be cracked or broken within their wrapped packaging due to shipping. This breakage is normal and does not reduce the effectiveness of the chlorine tabs. Harris Blue Solar Covers allow the sun to penetrate and warm the pool; unlike experimental solar covers that feature thick, reflective, aluminized coating and reflect the sun away from your pool. Harris 16 ft. x 40 ft. Rectangle Solar Covers are the environmentally friendly way to raise your pool temperature and maintain heat, without breaking the bank on your heating bill. Harris Blue Solar Covers allow the sunshine to penetrate and warm the pool; unlike experimental solar covers that feature thick, reflective, aluminized coating and reflect the sunshine away from your pool. input.product_name: Itza Badminton Set
input.description: Liven up your backyard or swimming pool with the Itza Badminton Set. Including all of the essentials necessary to begin a rousing game of badminton, this set has everything you need to turn the ordinary into the extraordinary. Versatility is the key as this portable badminton set can be maneuvered on the go. Regardless of whether youre looking to play at the beach, in the backyard or in the water itself, everything is possible. It includes a net, two telescoping poles, two rackets and two shuttlecocks.
